des:
From the same city as Ibiza's number 1 open-air club, and the most famous scene on the Mediterranean island comes Ushuaia.radio. The new innovative and cutting-edge FM and online radio station offering listeners the best selection of Dance, House, EDM and Tech House music.
With a presence in renowned cities such as Ibiza, Madrid, Milan and others in the rest of Europe, this radio station will bring collaborations and productions that seek to (re)create an incredible party atmosphere that leaves no one indifferent, direct from the Pitiusa island to the ears of your listeners in any corner of the world
